WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
narrator: ACL policy — who can talk to whom on the tailnet.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:15.000
narrator: the policy file is the Tailscale-format HUJSON document.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:25.000
narrator: tags scope rules to roles — tag:eng, tag:prod, and so on.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:35.000
narrator: a sample rule lets tag:eng reach tag:prod on port 22.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:45.000
narrator: headscale policy set publishes the file to the control plane.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:55.000
narrator: peers receive the new map within seconds — no restart.

00:00:55.000 --> 00:01:05.000
narrator: a connectivity test from an untagged host shows it is blocked.

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:15.000
narrator: ACL drift is recorded in the audit log for later review.
